Open up a Terminal (Applications->Accessories->Terminal) window, and type in it:

  sudo apt-get install python python-tk python-imaging python-imaging-tk
  chmod 0555 angrytux.py


|*******************************************|
|*  ____                    _              *|
|* |  _ \ _   _ _ __  _ __ (_)_ __   __ _  *|
